  "detailed_description": "A hero with no memory, and with a mysterious mask covering his face, <br>is thrown out into this land of unknown. <br>Reaching to an end of his journey, he discovers a truth that is hard to swallow - something terrifying about his true identity...<br><br>Explore a huge world with organically connected biomes of more than 300!<br>Terrifying monsters, multiple platform-actions and mysteries await you. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098080/extras/f01c7f51da4720d97f7903db99f1db50.poster.avif?t=1693963253\" width=554 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098080/extras/f01c7f51da4720d97f7903db99f1db50.webm?t=1693963253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098080/extras/f01c7f51da4720d97f7903db99f1db50.mp4?t=1693963253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Encounter 150+ monsters and final bosses using the aspects of discovered weapons!<br>- Blade-based attacks with an advantage of fast attack speed<br>- Sword-based attacks with massive-damaging attack<br>- Lance-based attacks with long reach and strategic gameplay<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098080/extras/cb9ef31b94d4dc4fe4f7565b545c5e28.poster.avif?t=1693963253\" width=554 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098080/extras/cb9ef31b94d4dc4fe4f7565b545c5e28.webm?t=1693963253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098080/extras/cb9ef31b94d4dc4fe4f7565b545c5e28.mp4?t=1693963253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect Occults spread all over the map to use the Forbidden Magic!<br>It is possible to build each player's main character into one's prefered battle type by using Occults and items found during the route.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098080/extras/708cb7f484c1fd14963b557e28f3e962.poster.avif?t=1693963253\" width=554 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098080/extras/708cb7f484c1fd14963b557e28f3e962.webm?t=1693963253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098080/extras/708cb7f484c1fd14963b557e28f3e962.mp4?t=1693963253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
